ack\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104unm1665702654361.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/unm1665702654361.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/unm1665702654361.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"unm1665702654361\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      DTD\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"unm1665702654361__dtd_311697\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A DTD is a Main Development Object that represents a Document Type Definition that\n      defines element declarations and a default mapping between the XML elements and Component\n      Entities and Fields.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"unm1665702654361__p_d95237e1_d95238e1_d95239e1\">It can be used to define the rules for the structure of an XML stream that is exchanged between components.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"unm1665702654361__topic_d63512e1_d63513e1_d63514e1_d63515e1_d63516e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1238967e56\">\n                     \n Characteristics\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">dtd</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"srw1665702550375.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/srw1665702550375.html\" title=\"A Main Development Object is a Development Object that has no parent object, is maintained using a dedicated editor, and can be saved and exported as a single unit, with all its children.\">Main Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">compiled DTD, readable DTD</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unm1665702654361__table_d10538e1_d10539e1_d10540e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">dtd:<var class=\"keyword varname\">EntityName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"unm1665702654361__topic_d63517e1_d63518e1_d63519e1_d63520e1_d63521e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1238967e233\">\n                     \n Specialization\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"unm1665702654361__p_d95246e1_d95247e1_d95248e1\">DTD specializes Main Development Object in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"unm1665702654361__li_d37520e1_d37521e1_d37522e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"unm1665702654361__p_d95249e1_d95250e1_d95251e1\">It has properties.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"unm1665702654361__li_d37523e1_d37524e1_d37525e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"unm1665702654361__p_d95252e1_d95253e1_d95254e1\">It contains no development objects or code\n                  containers.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"unm1665702654361__topic_d63522e1_d63523e1_d63524e1_d63525e1_d63526e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1238967e257\">\n                     \n Properties\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"unm1665702654361__li_d37526e1_d37527e1_d37528e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hlv1665702654431.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hlv1665702654431.html\" title=\"Unique name for the DTD.\">DTD Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"unm1665702654361__li_d37529e1_d37530e1_d37531e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"unm1665702654361__li_d37532e1_d37533e1_d37534e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jxv1665702654504.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jxv1665702654504.html\" title=\"Text field containing the DTD's element definitions.\">Definition</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"unm1665702654361__li_d37535e1_d37536e1_d37537e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tnh1665702654577.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tnh1665702654577.html\" title=\"Default mapping between element names in the DTD and Uniface field and entity names. This property contains an associative list ( GOLD ; separated) list of DTD element-Uniface name pairs.\">Default Mapping</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"unm1665702654361__li_d37538e1_d37539e1_d37540e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mxp1665702654645.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mxp1665702654645.html\" title=\"Name of the text file to which the Uniface DTD is compiled.\">File Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"unm1665702654361__li_d37541e1_d37542e1_d37543e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pxy1665702654725.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pxy1665702654725.html\" title=\"Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) for the Uniface DTD. This can be used by non-Uniface components to locate the DTD. Uniface can include this URI in XML streams based on the current DTD.\">External Reference</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"unm1665702654361__li_d37544e1_d37545e1_d37546e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bck1665702654827.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bck1665702654827.html\" title=\"Extended description of the global object.\">Comments</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uab1665702654218.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Uniface-Compliant DTDs</a><p>A Document Type Definition (DTD) defines rules for the structure of an XML stream. In Uniface, a DTD is a development object that includes DTD definitions and a default mapping between the XML elements defined by the DTD and Uniface component fields and entities. It can be used to define the rules for the structure of an XML stream that is exchanged between components.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qkw1665702654897.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Working with DTDs</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616353\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616353\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "DTD Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 DTD A DTD is a Main Development Object that represents a Document Type Definition that defines element declarations and a default mapping between the XML elements and Component Entities and Fields. It can be used to define the rules for the structure of an XML stream that is exchanged between components. Characteristics Characteristics Object type code: dtd Main Development Object? Yes Part of: — Contains: Property Generalization: Main Development Object Specializations: — Compilation Output: compiled DTD, readable DTD URI format: dtd: EntityName Specialization DTD specializes Main Development Object in the following ways: It has properties. It contains no development objects or code containers. Properties DTD Name Description Definition Default Mapping File Name External Reference Comments Related Links Uniface-Compliant DTDs A Document Type Definition (DTD) defines rules for the structure of an XML stream. In Uniface, a DTD is a development object that includes DTD definitions and a default mapping between the XML elements defined by the DTD and Uniface component fields and entities. It can be used to define the rules for the structure of an XML stream that is exchanged between components. Working with DTDs Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}